org.nlpcraft.model.intent

Interface NCIntentSolver.IntentCallback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Function<NCIntentSolverContext,NCQueryResult>, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    NCIntentSolver

    public static interface NCIntentSolver.IntentCallback
extends Function<NCIntentSolverContext,NCQueryResult>, Serializable
    Callback provided by the user for an intent when it is matched. It takes solver context as a parameter and should return query result. It can also throw either NCRejection or NCIntentSkip exceptions.
    See Also:
    NCIntentSolver.addIntent(INTENT, IntentCallback)
